Order everything you want to eat tonight.

973
01:01:22,765 --> 01:01:24,976
On behalf of the company, I…

974
01:01:29,647 --> 01:01:30,773
As a manager,

975
01:01:31,607 --> 01:01:32,733
I'll pay for everything!

976
01:01:33,901 --> 01:01:35,903
Come on!

977
01:01:35,987 --> 01:01:37,238
Come on!

978
01:01:37,321 --> 01:01:38,864
Mr. No!

979
01:01:39,365 --> 01:01:41,325
"Gang Da-eul, Oh Pyeong-hwa,

980
01:01:41,409 --> 01:01:42,743
Cheon Sa-rang"?

981
01:01:43,327 --> 01:01:44,286
The kind Ms. Sa-rang?

982
01:01:44,370 --> 01:01:45,705
What is this?

983
01:01:45,788 --> 01:01:49,917
The number one employees
of King Distribution, Air, and Hotel.

984
01:01:50,001 --> 01:01:51,794
They are King Group's best employees.

985
01:01:51,877 --> 01:01:54,130
Prepare an overseas trip
as their incentive.

986
01:01:54,213 --> 01:01:56,215
The remaining employees
will be sent in turn.

987
01:01:56,298 --> 01:01:59,552
Why are you so concerned
about the employees' incentive trips?

988
01:02:00,469 --> 01:02:03,097
The company should reward them
for their performance.

989
01:02:03,180 --> 01:02:04,515
Isn't that a given?

990
01:02:05,141 --> 01:02:07,101
I've never seen
such an openhanded company.

991
01:02:11,772 --> 01:02:12,857
There's one right here.

992
01:02:13,399 --> 01:02:15,359
- Ms. Gu's approval is needed, right?
- No.

993
01:02:15,943 --> 01:02:17,945
I'm making all the decisions
about the hotel.

994
01:02:18,029 --> 01:02:20,906
With employees from Distribution and Air,
it's the group's issue.

995
01:02:20,990 --> 01:02:23,034
- Will you be okay?
- You may proceed.

996
01:02:23,117 --> 01:02:24,994
I'll take responsibility.

997
01:02:25,077 --> 01:02:26,537
They are our group's best employees,

998
01:02:26,620 --> 01:02:30,374
so it needs to be the finest
and most luxurious experience.

999
01:02:38,549 --> 01:02:39,508
Me?

1000
01:02:43,679 --> 01:02:44,513
"A nice trip"?

1001
01:02:44,597 --> 01:02:46,515
WE'LL REWARD YOU WITH A NICE TRIP

1002
01:02:47,767 --> 01:02:48,934
What?

1003
01:02:49,018 --> 01:02:52,938
"Ms. Oh Pyeong-hwa, thank you
for your devotion and hard work."

1004
01:02:53,439 --> 01:02:55,524
"We'll reward you with a nice trip."

1005
01:02:56,776 --> 01:02:57,735
Congratulations.

1006
01:02:57,818 --> 01:03:00,529
The best staff of the group
are being given incentive trips.

1007
01:03:01,197 --> 01:03:02,323
Congratulations.

1008
01:03:11,123 --> 01:03:12,166
Thank you.

1009
01:03:15,878 --> 01:03:18,506
They're leaving tomorrow.
Is everything ready?

1010
01:03:18,589 --> 01:03:19,632
Of course.

1011
01:03:19,715 --> 01:03:22,343
They will experience
the best trip of their lives.

1012
01:03:22,426 --> 01:03:23,761
You'll be shocked.

1013
