1015
01:03:30,684 --> 01:03:32,394
No, this is what I usually do

1016
01:03:32,478 --> 01:03:35,439
as King Group's best assistant.
You know that, right?

1017
01:03:44,490 --> 01:03:46,867
- Are you sick?
- No, I'm perfectly fine.

1018
01:03:52,665 --> 01:03:54,083
I'll drive you home safely.

1019
01:04:11,767 --> 01:04:12,601
I'm so excited.

1020
01:04:14,645 --> 01:04:15,980
- I'm so happy!
- Hey!

1021
01:04:17,898 --> 01:04:19,733
Oh my. Mr. No!

1022
01:04:19,817 --> 01:04:20,734
You're here.

1023
01:04:20,818 --> 01:04:22,695
This is all thanks to you.

1024
01:04:22,778 --> 01:04:23,863
I didn't do anything.

1025
01:04:23,946 --> 01:04:26,740
We're going on this trip
because you told the higher-ups.

1026
01:04:26,824 --> 01:04:28,409
You'll be blessed.

1027
01:04:28,492 --> 01:04:30,035
Thank you so much.

1028
01:04:31,245 --> 01:04:34,290
For this trip,
let's forget about everything

1029
01:04:34,373 --> 01:04:36,167
and make this a happy, exciting,

1030
01:04:36,250 --> 01:04:37,668
