1036
01:04:51,879 --> 01:04:52,922
Let's go then.

1037
01:05:01,743 --> 01:05:03,161
I'm so happy.

1038
01:05:03,745 --> 01:05:04,913
What should we eat first?

1039
01:05:04,996 --> 01:05:06,414
That's a good question.

1040
01:05:11,294 --> 01:05:12,462
Head…

1041
01:05:13,797 --> 01:05:16,925
Manager!

1042
01:05:21,304 --> 01:05:22,597
Be quiet.

1043
01:05:22,681 --> 01:05:23,807
- Who is he?
- Someone he knows?

1044
01:05:23,890 --> 01:05:24,724
Why are you here?

1045
01:05:24,808 --> 01:05:26,434
This is a trip
for King Group's best employees.

1046
01:05:26,518 --> 01:05:27,644
I'm the best assistant.

1047
01:05:27,727 --> 01:05:31,272
I get what you're saying.
I'll send you on a trip next time. So go--

1048
01:05:31,356 --> 01:05:33,525
That's ridiculous. I need to assist you.

1049
01:05:33,608 --> 01:05:35,151
Assist me with what?

1050
01:05:35,235 --> 01:05:36,945
- Just leave.
- Who are you?

1051
01:05:41,282 --> 01:05:43,576
- Hi, Sa-rang.
- Hello.

1052
01:05:44,619 --> 01:05:46,621
-It is an honor to finally meet
-He works at the hotel.

1053
01:05:46,705 --> 01:05:47,872
the people who were on the papers.

1054
01:05:47,956 --> 01:05:49,582
Let me introduce myself. I'm--

1055
01:05:49,666 --> 01:05:50,625
He is

1056
01:05:52,210 --> 01:05:54,337
the man behind this incentive trip,

1057
01:05:54,421 --> 01:05:56,047
Department Manager Yoo Sang-sik.

1058
01:05:59,426 --> 01:06:01,010
What are you talking about?

1059
01:06:04,055 --> 01:06:06,057
Let's introduce ourselves again.

1060
01:06:06,141 --> 01:06:09,185
This is Mr. Yoo Sang-sik.
He's a department manager.

1061
01:06:10,854 --> 01:06:11,813
And I'm

1062
01:06:12,397 --> 01:06:13,398
Mr. No.

1063
01:06:13,481 --> 01:06:15,567
Thank you, Mr. Yoo.

1064
