01:06:32,167 --> 01:06:33,501
So can you go over there?

1074
01:06:34,502 --> 01:06:36,463
Let me introduce myself again properly.

1075
01:06:36,546 --> 01:06:39,132
I am the department manager
in charge of this trip,

1076
01:06:39,215 --> 01:06:40,967
No… I mean, Yoo Sang-sik.

1077
01:06:41,050 --> 01:06:42,177
It's nice to meet you.

1078
01:06:46,097 --> 01:06:48,516
The concept of this trip is "We go hard."

1079
01:06:49,184 --> 01:06:50,727
When we eat, go hard.

1080
01:06:50,810 --> 01:06:52,437
When we have fun, go hard.

1081
01:06:52,520 --> 01:06:54,314
- All together…
- We go hard!

1082
01:06:54,397 --> 01:06:55,273
You're so energetic.

1083
01:06:56,858 --> 01:06:59,819
But Mr. No,
why do you have your mouth shut?

1084
01:07:05,492 --> 01:07:07,494
Just act like I'm not here, please.

1085
01:07:07,577 --> 01:07:09,287
Unity is key for this trip.

1086
01:07:09,370 --> 01:07:11,080
Individual activities are not allowed.

1087
01:07:11,164 --> 01:07:13,583
We'll set off after shouting our chant.

1088
01:07:14,209 --> 01:07:16,002
- When we eat…
- Go hard!

1089
01:07:16,085 --> 01:07:17,837
- When we have fun…
- Go hard!

1090
01:07:17,921 --> 01:07:19,714
- All together, we go hard!
- We go hard!

1091
01:07:19,798 --> 01:07:21,758
Okay. Let's go!

1092
01:07:32,477 --> 01:07:33,728
Why aren't you coming?

1093
01:07:33,812 --> 01:07:37,023
I'm not letting Mr. No get away with this.

1094
01:07:37,106 --> 01:07:38,441
I thought he was Mr. Yoo.

1095
01:07:39,400 --> 01:07:41,069
His enthusiasm is nice. Let's go.

1096
01:07:44,239 --> 01:07:45,281
Mr. No!

1097
01:07:45,824 --> 01:07:48,076
- Hurry up!
- Hurry up!

1098
01:07:48,159 --> 01:07:49,786
Okay. Coming.

1099
01:07:50,453 --> 01:07:51,371
I'm coming.

1100
01:07:51,454 --> 01:07:53,540
Mr. No, let's go!

1101
01:07:54,541 --> 01:07:57,669
Mr. No, let's go!

1102
01:08:08,972 --> 01:08:11,975
KING THE LAND

1103
01:08:44,090 --> 01:08:44,924
<i>Go hard!</i>

1104
01:08:45,008 --> 01:08:46,009
- Go hard!
- Go hard!

1105
01:08:47,343 --> 01:08:49,137
<i>Let me announce today's schedule.</i>

1106
01:08:49,220 --> 01:08:50,179
<i>What about free time?</i>

1107
01:08:50,263 --> 01:08:51,848
<i>There's no free time on a group tour.</i>

1108
01:08:51,931 --> 01:08:53,683
<i>- Let's get out of here.
- Now?</i>

1109
01:08:53,766 --> 01:08:54,767
Now.

1110
01:08:56,728 --> 01:08:57,645
<i>A trip?</i>

1111
01:08:57,729 --> 01:09:00,648
<i>How could something in King Group
be carried out without my knowledge?</i>

1112
01:09:00,732 --> 01:09:03,401
<i>But I keep wanting more.</i>

1113
01:09:03,484 --> 01:09:07,071
<i>I feel so happy that I begin to wonder
if I'm allowed this much happiness.</i>

1114
01:09:07,155 --> 01:09:11,367
<i>I keep hoping that
I'll continue to be this happy.</i>

1115
01:09:11,451 --> 01:09:14,245
<i>I'll make every day of yours
filled with happiness.</i>

